                                <div class="phototagleft">
                                  
                                </div>
                                                          </div>
                                                                                            <p style="margin-bottom:16px"><strong>Miho Kinnas</strong> is the author of <em>Waiting for Sunset to Bury Red Camellias</em> (Free Verse Press.) She leads a workshop based on Japanese poetic forms at <a href="https://writers.com/instructor/miho-kinnas">writers.com</a>. Her <a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/interviews/poet-translator-mirror-conversation-miho-kinnas-renee-h-shea">conversation</a> with Renee H. Shea for <em>WLT</em> appeared in 2023.</p>

